
This implementation provides a complete solution for the Document-to-Presentation Converter assignment, featuring:

1. A user-friendly Streamlit interface
2. Support for multiple document formats (PDF, DOCX, TXT)
3. Image extraction and handling
4. Integration with Gemini AI for content processing
5. PowerPoint generation with proper formatting
6. Error handling and cleanup
7. Clear project structure and documentation

To run the project, users need to:
1. Install the required dependencies
2. Set up their Gemini API key
3. Run the Streamlit application

The code is modular and follows good practices for maintainability and extensibility.